stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> RequestPIN : Start Zwei-Schritte-Verifizierung
    RequestPIN --> EnterPIN : User prompted for PIN
    EnterPIN --> VerifyPIN : User submits PIN
    VerifyPIN --> Success : PIN is correct
    VerifyPIN --> Failure : PIN is incorrect
    Failure --> EnterPIN : Retry
    Success --> [*] : End Zwei-Schritte-Verifizierung